data.description: Unveil a captivating Craftsman gem on a fully fenced half-acre lot, offering elegant hardwood floors throughout. The living room features a cozy pellet stove setup and built-in shelving. The kitchen, with ample storage and dual pantries, meets all your cooking needs. An accommodating dining area surprises with extra storage, while the spacious family room opens to a backyard oasis. Notable features include a covered deck for outdoor enjoyment, a well-equipped 792 SqFt garage/shop with plumbing for a possible ADU, and a storage shed. Close to shopping, dining, I-5, and JBLM, this Craftsman home balances charm, security, and room for all your dreams. Your ideal home awaits – seize the opportunity!
